OL,3,CHealth Secretary promises compensation
OL,4,Cfor Sodium Valproate victims
OL,6,FThe Health Secretary has promised to
OL,7,Fbring in a compensation scheme before
OL,8,Fthe next general election for the
OL,9,Fvictims of a medical scandal that left
OL,10,Fthousands of babies disabled.
OL,12,FMothers prescribed the drug Sodium
OL,13,FValproate during pregnancy as an
OL,14,Feffective treatment for epilepsy,
OL,15,Fbipolar disorder and to prevent
OL,16,Fmigraines were never warned of the
OL,17,Frisks to their unborn children.
OL,19,FAs a result, over the past 40 years,
OL,20,Fthousands of babies were born with
OL,21,Fbirth defects and developmental delays.
