OL,3,CHealth Secretary promises compensation
OL,4,Cfor Sodium Valproate victims
OL,6,FIn 2024 "urgent" payments were
OL,7,Frecommended by the patient safety
OL,8,Fcommissioner, which set out
OL,9,Frecommendations for a compensation
OL,10,Fscheme for those affected.
OL,12,FThe Hughes Report - published on 7
OL,13,FFebruary 2024 - examined the impact
OL,14,Fthe medication had on pregnant women
OL,15,Fand their unborn children.
OL,17,FBut so far, despite the
OL,18,Frecommendations, no payments have been
OL,19,Fmade.
