OL,3,CHealth Secretary promises compensation
OL,4,Cfor Sodium Valproate victims
OL,6,FNow Health Secretary Wes Streeting has
OL,7,Ftold ITV Granada Reports that he will
OL,8,Fbring in the scheme before the next
OL,9,Fgeneral election.
OL,11,F"We (the Government) are considering
OL,12,Fvery carefully the recommendations of
OL,13,Fthe Hughes Report," Mr Streeting said.
OL,15,F"It is absolute vital that we get this
OL,16,Fright, that we deal with this
OL,17,Finjustice in a way that is transparent
OL,18,Fand in a way that is fair."
