OL,3,CHealth Secretary promises compensation
OL,4,Cfor Sodium Valproate victims
OL,6,FAs well as the report recommending a
OL,7,Fcompensation scheme, it also suggested
OL,8,Fquicker interim payments in June 2025
OL,9,Fto help families that have been left
OL,10,Fin financial crisis.
OL,12,FMr Streeting continued: "This is a
OL,13,Fcomplex issue. I think what the Hughes
OL,14,FReport laid bare was the nature of
OL,15,Fthis scandal and the harm that has
OL,16,Fbeen caused."
