OL,3,CHealth Secretary promises compensation
OL,4,Cfor Sodium Valproate victims
OL,6,FWhen challenged by Political
OL,7,FCorrespondent Lise McNally about why
OL,8,Fthe Government still have not given
OL,9,Fthe families interim payments, Mr
OL,10,FStreeting said: "I am working with
OL,11,Fcolleagues, right across Government to
OL,12,Fmake sure that we respond to the
OL,13,FHughes Report that is fair to the
OL,14,Fmothers of this scandal."
OL,16,FBut that is the line two mothers from
OL,17,FLancashire say they have heard too
OL,18,Fmany times before.
