OL,3,CHealth Secretary promises compensation
OL,4,Cfor Sodium Valproate victims
OL,6,FEmma Murphy said: "Our babies were
OL,7,Fvictims from the moment they were born
OL,8,Fand they continue to be victimised by
OL,9,Fthis government and gaslit."
OL,11,FJanet Williams added: "We feel very
OL,12,Flet down. We were hoping that when a
OL,13,FLabour Government took over, things
OL,14,Fwould be different but obviously we
OL,15,Fhave just been so wrong with that."
OL,17,FLabour MPs are among those calling for
OL,18,Fthe Government to respond to the
OL,19,FHughes Report recommendations.
