OL,3,CHealth Secretary promises compensation
OL,4,Cfor Sodium Valproate victims
OL,6,FEllesmere Port MP Justin Madders
OL,7,Fpreviously said that Sodium Valproate
OL,8,Fvictims have "spent their lives
OL,9,Ffighting for their kids".
OL,11,FMeanwhile, the Labour MP for Morecambe
OL,12,Fand Lunesdale said that "the can has
OL,13,Fbeen kicked down the road for too
OL,14,Flong."
OL,16,F"Given how long families have
OL,17,Fcampaigned for justice, I can well
OL,18,Funderstand why and they are critical,
OL,19,Fhaving waited so long and I have got
OL,20,Fto take that criticism on the chin.
